# AI/LLM Integration Patterns

Before building or modifying any AI features, solving algorithms, or automated scheduling, you must read the core architecture documentation:

- Read `docs/architecture/04-ai-and-scheduling.md` to understand the CP-SAT solver and candidate filtering architecture.

## AI Service Structure (Phase 4)

```
src/server/services/ai/
├── openai-client.ts           # OpenAI API wrapper
├── scheduling-agent.service.ts # CP Solver Orchestrator
├── message-agent.service.ts    # Agentic SMS intent parsing (Phase 4)
